text: Twelfth Avenue is a short portion of the West Side Highway in Manhattan. Twelfth Avenue could also refer to: *13th Avenue (Borough Park), the commercial center of Borough Park, Brooklyn *12th Avenue South Bridge, a permanent steel bridges in Seattle. *Clinton Street/Southeast 12th Avenue station, a train station in Portland, Oregon. *Washington/Southeast 12th Avenue station, a train station in Hillsboro, Oregon. *Judah and 12th Avenue station, a train station in San Francisco, California.
title: Twelfth Avenue (disambiguation)
